data.description: Come and see this move in ready beauty in the highly sought after Coconut Cay community in Miami Gardens. This two-story home has a new roof and showcases an inviting open layout that is perfect for entertaining guest.  With four spacious bedrooms and an amazing loft, this beauty stands as the third largest model within the community.      Convenience meets luxury as this property offers seamless access to both I-95 and the Turnpike, ensuring effortless travel.  Embrace the vibrant energy of Miami with nearby attractions such as the iconic Hard Rock Stadium and Aventura Mall, all just moments away from your doorsteps.    Note:  Property will not be available until late December, maybe sooner.
